  "body": "Currently, the `quantile` operator is provided, but there's no `median`. The `median` according to https://prometheus.io/docs/practices/histograms/ is trivially `quantile(0.5, ...)`. Can you please consider either adding a new `median` operator to do this, or adding a note to `quantile` in the docs https://prometheus.io/docs/prometheus/latest/querying/operators/ for users that don't know this?\r\n\r\nThank you.",
